column2: Okay, we have another important part of the tour. I'm going to give you some info you're going to need.
We're going to visit the Roster.
Launch the Roster app from the desktop.
You'll find a lot of cool info about our crew here. Check out the page about Saniel.
Click on Saniel's pic to read about him.
Oh Snap! You've already read all about Saniel. Awesome.
You found it. Excellent. Quite fascinating, isn't he?
Check out the others too! Then come stop by the Clubhouse again.
I'll be in the Clubhouse. Just come get me whenever.
